---
// src/pages/about/index.astro
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const pageTitle = "About — Abba Unveiled";
const pageDesc =
  "Why Abba Unveiled exists, who W.R. Selvig is, and how this message invites you to know the Father Jesus revealed.";
---

<BaseLayout title={pageTitle} description={pageDesc}>
  <!-- HERO with background + overlay + centered card -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero__overlay"></div>
    <div class="hero__container">
      <div class="card">
        <header class="card__header">
          <h1>About Abba Unveiled</h1>
          <p class="subtitle">
            Why we exist, who W.R. Selvig is, and how this message invites you to know the Father Jesus revealed.
          </p>
        </header>

        <article class="card__content">
          <h2 id="why">Why Abba Unveiled?</h2>
          <p>
            For many believers, there’s a quiet tension: the Father that Jesus reveals feels very different from the God
            described in much of the Old Testament. For years, I carried that same fracture. I trusted Jesus, but when I
            thought of the Father, I hesitated.
          </p>
          <p>
            <em>Abba Unveiled</em> was born out of my search to heal that fracture. As I sought Jesus, He led me into answers
            I didn’t expect—answers that revealed a good, kind, merciful Father who is better than we’ve been told. This site,
            and my book <em>The Yahweh Deception</em>, exist to lift the veil and invite you into a fresh encounter with Abba.
          </p>

          <h2>Who I Am</h2>
          <p>
            I’m W.R. Selvig—author, podcaster, and lifelong follower of Jesus. For over forty years I’ve pursued Him through
            prayer, research, and encounters.  I never planned to write this book—Jesus asked me to share what He showed me so others could find the same healing and freedom.
          </p>

          <h2>What You’ll Find Here</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Theology</strong> that challenges assumptions and lifts veils.</li>
            <li><strong>Spiritual practices</strong> that restore intimacy with the Father.</li>
            <li><strong>Personal encounters</strong> from my journey that may resonate with yours.</li>
            <li><strong>Podcasts &amp; resources</strong> to support your walk with Abba.</li>
          </ul>

          <blockquote>
            “This isn’t about tearing down faith. It’s about strengthening it—freeing believers from fear and inviting them
            into the love Jesus always pointed to.”
          </blockquote>

          <h2>A Time of Unveiling</h2>
          <p>
            We’re living in a new era of revelation. Across the world, corruption is being exposed—in politics, education, and
            religion. It’s uncomfortable, but necessary: only when deception is revealed can healing and new structures rise. I
            believe this unveiling includes the Father’s own character, long obscured by fear and tradition. The bandage is
            coming off. Sons and daughters are learning to trust Abba again.
          </p>

          <h2>Listen: “Who is W.R. Selvig?” (Podcast Episode 4)</h2>
          <p>Prefer to hear the story? Listen to the episode below where I share the dream, the numbers, and the healing.</p>

          <div class="player">
            <iframe
              src="https://widget.spreaker.com/player?episode_id=67835208&theme=light&playlist=false&autoplay=false&chapters=false&download=true"
              width="100%"
              height="160"
              frameborder="0"
              loading="lazy"
              title="Podcast player: Episode 4 - Who is W.R. Selvig?"
            ></iframe>
          </div>

          <h2>The Invitation</h2>
          <p>
            This journey isn’t about controversy—it’s about clarity, freedom, and intimacy with the true Father. Come meet Abba
            as Jesus revealed Him: good, kind, merciful, and trustworthy.
          </p>

          <p class="cta-wrap">
  <a class="btn-cta btn-cta--slim" href="/store" aria-label="Go to Store to get The Yahweh Deception">
    Get the Book: The Yahweh Deception
  </a>
</p>

        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* HERO background */
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 80vh;
    padding: 48px 16px 72px;
    background-image: url("/images/stars-northern.png");
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
  }
  /* overlay for readability */
  .hero__overlay {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.55), rgba(0,0,0,0.55));
    z-index: 0;
  }
  .hero__container {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex; align-items: flex-start; justify-content: center;
  }

  /* CARD */
  .card {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 960px;
    background: #fff;
    color: #111;
    border-radius: 24px;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
    border: 1px solid rgba(17,17,17,0.08);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .card__header {
    padding: 28px 28px 0 28px;
  }
  .card__header h1 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .subtitle {
    margin-top: 8px;
    color: #4b5563;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }
  .card__content {
    padding: 20px 28px 32px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }
  .card__content h2 {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    margin: 1.6rem 0 0.6rem;
    line-height: 1.25;
  }
  .card__content p { margin: 0.8rem 0; }
  .card__content ul { padding-left: 1.2rem; margin: 0.8rem 0 1.2rem; }
  .card__content li { margin: 0.4rem 0; }
  blockquote {
    margin: 1.2rem 0;
    padding: 0.9rem 1rem;
    background: #f7f7f9;
    border-left: 4px solid #e0e0e7;
    color: #333;
    border-radius: 6px;
  }

  /* Player spacing */
  .player { margin: 1rem 0 1.5rem; }
  .player iframe { border-radius: 10px; }

  /* CTA button (fallback if you don't already have .btn-cta globally) */
  .cta-wrap { margin-top: 1.2rem; }
  .btn-cta {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem;
    border-radius: 9999px;
    font-weight: 600;
    border: 1px solid #111;
    color: #111;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: transform 0.12s ease, background 0.12s ease;
    background: #fff;
  }
  .btn-cta:hover { background: #111; color: #fff; transform: translateY(-1px); }

  /* Responsive tweaks */
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .card__header { padding: 20px 18px 0; }
    .card__content { padding: 14px 18px 22px; }
    .card__header h1 { font-size: 1.8rem; }
  }
  /* center the CTA and make it slimmer */
.cta-wrap { margin-top: 1.2rem; text-align: center; }

.btn-cta--slim{
  display:inline-flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; text-align:center;
  padding:.5rem 1rem; font-size:1rem; line-height:1; border-radius:9999px; white-space:nowrap;
}

</style>
